snippet.title: Ridiculous Fishing
snippet.description: Ridiculous Fishing is a fun and funny diversion, with upgrades that suck you in, and the kind of arcade action that makes it easy to recommend to any iOS gamer.

snippet.title: Duet Game
snippet.description: Easy to learn, but extremely difficult to master, Duet Game is a must-have for serious gamers who don't mind repetition while going for the proverbial perfect run.

snippet.title: Fire Game Controller
snippet.description: Get ready for living-room gaming, Amazon-style: a new controller aims to bring games to the big screen with Fire TV.

snippet.title: Concussion bot to debut at Northern Arizona football game
snippet.description: Mayo Clinic researchers are gearing up to test their new teleconcussion robot on the sidelines of tonight's Northern Arizona University football game.

snippet.title: The Walk Fitness Tracker Game
snippet.description: Despite its complex interface and high download price, The Walk: Fitness Tracker Game is an excellent way to make your daily walk interesting again.

snippet.title: BlueStacks partners with Big Fish on mobile game integration
snippet.description: Pact will allow Android developers to monetize casual game maker Big Fish's 4,000 PC games.

snippet.title: Sky+ HD boxes get tasty new homepage from today
snippet.description: Sky's giving its programme guide and apps a new lease of life with a smart TV-style homepage, rolling out to customers from today.

snippet.title: Ouya Game Console
snippet.description: Despite its low price and free-to-try system, the Ouya fails to reach its potential as a disruptive alternative platform.

snippet.title: Apple urges veto of Arizona 'antigay' bill
snippet.description: The bill faces a decision by the governor of Arizona just as Apple is gearing up its new sapphire plant in the city of Mesa.

snippet.title: New Jersey joins Arizona and Texas in Tesla sales ban
snippet.description: New Jersey's Motor Vehicles Commission approved a rule today that bans Tesla's direct sales of vehicles to consumers.
